---
import Layout from "@astro/layouts/Layout.astro";
import SimplePage from "@astro/components/SimplePage.astro";
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — PromptAndGo" description="How PromptAndGo collects, uses, and protects your data.">
  <SimplePage title="Privacy Policy" updated="May 2026">
    <p>We respect your privacy. This policy explains what we collect, why, and how to control it.</p>
    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Account info</strong>: email, name, basic profile.</li>
      <li><strong>Prompts you create</strong>: stored privately under your account unless you publish them.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data</strong>: pages visited, optimisations run, errors. Used to improve the service.</li>
      <li><strong>Payment info</strong>: handled by Stripe; we never see card numbers.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>How we use it</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To provide and improve the service</li>
      <li>To send transactional emails (signup, receipts, security)</li>
      <li>To send product updates if you opt in</li>
      <li>To respond to support requests</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Sharing</h2>
    <p>We share data with: Supabase (our database / auth), Stripe (payments), Resend (email), the AI provider you choose for each request (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, etc.). We don't sell your data.</p>
    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>You can export or delete your data anytime from <a href="/account">account settings</a>. EU/UK residents: see GDPR rights below.</p>
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies for auth and basic analytics. See our <a href="/cookies">cookie policy</a>.</p>
    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>Encryption at rest and in transit. Sensitive subscriber data is encrypted with a separate key. Two-factor authentication recommended on your account.</p>
    <h2>Children</h2>
    <p>The service is for users 13+ (16+ in EU). We don't knowingly collect data from younger children.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Privacy questions: <a href="/contact?topic=privacy">contact us</a>.</p>
  </SimplePage>
</Layout>
